---
import Layout from "@/layouts/Layout.astro";
import Container from "@/components/container.astro";
import Sectionhead from "@/components/sectionhead.astro";
import { Icon } from "astro-icon/components";
---

<Layout title="Data & Analytics | AnichLabs OÜ">
  <Container>
    <Sectionhead>
      <Fragment slot="title">Data & Analytics</Fragment>
      <Fragment slot="desc">Analytics, statistical modelling, and evidence work for healthcare and regulated environments.</Fragment>
    </Sectionhead>

    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl mt-16">
      <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed text-lg">
        Hospitals, clinics, and health-tech companies collect enormous volumes of data. Most of it sits in silos, legacy systems, or poorly structured databases. Without the right analytical infrastructure, that data generates reports nobody reads and decisions based on gut feeling rather than evidence.
      </p>
      <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed text-lg mt-4">
        AnichLabs OÜ designs and builds data pipelines, statistical models, and dashboards tailored to healthcare contexts. Every solution is built with GDPR-compliant data handling from the start: pseudonymisation, access controls, and audit trails included. Outputs are designed for the clinical and operational teams who will actually use them.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl mt-12">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-6">What we deliver</h2>
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-xl p-6 border border-slate-100">
          <Icon name="uil:database" class="w-7 h-7 mb-3" style="color: #003399" />
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">Data Pipelines</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm">Reproducible cleaning and transformation pipelines, designed for reliable analytical outputs and ongoing automation.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-xl p-6 border border-slate-100">
          <Icon name="uil:chart-line" class="w-7 h-7 mb-3" style="color: #003399" />
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">Statistical Modelling</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm">Descriptive, inferential, and predictive modelling in Python or R, with clinical validation of endpoints.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-xl p-6 border border-slate-100">
          <Icon name="uil:chart-pie" class="w-7 h-7 mb-3" style="color: #003399" />
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">Dashboards and Reports</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm">Custom dashboards in Metabase, Power BI, or bespoke tools, plus written reports for leadership and clinical governance.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-xl p-6 border border-slate-100">
          <Icon name="uil:lock" class="w-7 h-7 mb-3" style="color: #003399" />
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">GDPR-Compliant by Design</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm">Pseudonymisation, data minimisation, and access controls applied throughout, with documentation suitable for DPO review.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl mt-16">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-6">Common questions</h2>
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
        <details class="bg-slate-50 border border-slate-100 rounded-xl p-5 group">
          <summary class="font-semibold text-gray-800 cursor-pointer list-none flex justify-between items-center text-sm">
            Our data is messy and incomplete. Can you still help?
            <Icon name="uil:angle-down" class="w-5 h-5 text-slate-400 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform" />
          </summary>
          <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm mt-3">Yes. Messy data is the norm in healthcare, not the exception. We start with a data audit to give you honest expectations about what your data can and cannot support.</p>
        </details>
        <details class="bg-slate-50 border border-slate-100 rounded-xl p-5 group">
          <summary class="font-semibold text-gray-800 cursor-pointer list-none flex justify-between items-center text-sm">
            What tools do you use?
            <Icon name="uil:angle-down" class="w-5 h-5 text-slate-400 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform" />
          </summary>
          <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm mt-3">Python and R for modelling, PostgreSQL and pgvector for storage, Metabase and Power BI for dashboards. We pick tools based on what your team can maintain, not what is fashionable.</p>
        </details>
        <details class="bg-slate-50 border border-slate-100 rounded-xl p-5 group">
          <summary class="font-semibold text-gray-800 cursor-pointer list-none flex justify-between items-center text-sm">
            Will our team be able to maintain what you build?
            <Icon name="uil:angle-down" class="w-5 h-5 text-slate-400 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform" />
          </summary>
          <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm mt-3">Yes. Every project includes documentation and a handover session. We optimise for transparency and maintainability, not for keeping you dependent on us.</p>
        </details>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl mt-16 mb-10 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800">Ready to make sense of your healthcare data?</h2>
      <p class="text-slate-500 mt-3">Book a free 30-minute call and we will scope what is feasible with your data.</p>
      <a href="https://calendly.com/chris-anichlabs/30min" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
        class="mt-6 inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-white font-semibold px-6 py-3 rounded-lg transition-colors"
        style="background-color: #003399">
        <Icon name="uil:calendar-alt" class="w-5 h-5" />
        Book a Free Call
      </a>
    </div>

  </Container>
</Layout>